5009,Truth or Consequences,"['Singing', 'Storytelling']","['Bluffing', 'Humor', 'Movies / TV / Radio theme', 'Party Game', 'Trivia']",Editions vary in execution but one player asks a trivia question or riddle of the one or more of the other players. A player scores by answering correctly and the turn passes to the next player. If the player fails to give the correct answer then the player must complete a physical stunt to score. Players takes turns being quizzed and quizzer.<br/><br/>The game ends after a predetemined number of rounds or after someone reaches the goal score. Highest score wins.<br/><br/>This a faithful translation of the television (and radio) game show with the same name.<br/><br/>,1955,,,
