5067,Lifetime,"['Hand Management', 'Push Your Luck']","['Card Game', 'Trivia']","In Lifetime, each player must try to correctly estimate the lifetime of a famous person and must place a year card between the birth and death year of that person. In clockwise order, each player places one of cards at the card row in the middle of the table, taking care not to go under the birth year or over the death year of the famous person.  <br/>  <br/>Whoever can't place it correctly, must take all the previously played cards. The winner is the player who either successfully places all of his cards in one round or who has taken the least cards at the end of the game.<br/><br/>",1996,,,
5068,Flinke Finger,"['Betting and Bluffing', 'Hand Management', 'Set Collection']",['Card Game'],"Flinke Finger is a collection of 3 different games:<br/><br/>REFLEX is a fast, exciting card laying game.  <br/>Goal of the game: Each player tries to get rid of his cards as quickly as possible and, by doing so, to score points.<br/><br/>TRAF is more tactical, but, still easy to understand.  <br/>Goal of the game:  Each player tries to get as many points as possible by skillfully combining his cards.<br/><br/>PUKO is a poker variant with interesting special rules.  <br/>Goal of the game: Each player tries to score as many points as possible with his card combinations.<br/><br/>",1999,,,
