ayer handy.)<br/>     8 Character Packets which contain the information for each of your guests.<br/>    4 evidence baggies containing actual physical evidence your guests will want to examine. These include the two torn playing cards found on the dead bodies, a buffalo nickel (of all things... hmmm.) and an interesting letter found folded up in Percival's pocket.<br/>    Other supporting materials, including a map of the island, a floor plan of the house, a timeline of events, etc.<br/>    Nametags for your guests with their character's name.<br/>    Game instructions for the host and the guests.<br/><br/><br/>",0,,,
