5207,Sammy The White House Mouse,['Roll / Spin and Move'],"['Animals', ""Children's Game"", 'Educational']","The object of Sammy The White House Mouseis to be the first mouse to the White House.<br/>Game Rules<br/><br/>Contents:<br/><br/>    4 Colored mice<br/>    7 Star cards<br/>    4 Cheese cards<br/>    6 Golden Horns<br/>    7 Blind Man Glasses<br/>    Game Board<br/><br/><br/>PREPARATION:<br/>Carefully separate cards from box platform.&nbsp; Mix cards and place face down, on spot marked CARDS.<br/>RULES:<br/>1.&nbsp; Pick your color mouse to move throughout the game.<br/>2.&nbsp; Place all mice at START.<br/>3.&nbsp; All players draw cards from CARD pile until one player draws the Golden Horn.&nbsp; That player goes first.&nbsp; Other players follow in turn, clockwise.&nbsp; Collect cards drawn, mix again and replace cards on board.<br/>4.&nbsp; Player going first draws one card, then moves mouse forward to next space on the board which has the same picture as card drawn.&nbsp; Player then places this card in a discard pile.<br/>5.&nbsp; All players follow in turn.<br/>6.&nbsp; Another player landing on the same space as you, sends you backwards to the next matching space on the board.&nbsp; Example:&nbsp; If you are on the cheese, you must go back tot he previous cheese space.<br/>7.&nbsp; When cards are used, mix discards and use over again.<br/>8.&nbsp; Be first to the White House and WIN!<br/><br/>",1977,,,
