a Guests Include: (Non-Suspects)<br/><br/>Porter Stout - The local mayor and a man who knows a thing or two about beer-drinking. Porter has worked hard to get national publicity for the festival and will stop at nothing to ensure its success. A pompous politician, he likes to work the crowd at every opportunity. Good hand-shaker.<br/><br/>Heidi Stein - A special guest from Munich, Germany, Heidi is at the Beer Festival to promote the upcoming Octoberfest celebrations in her country. A past polka champion, Heidi is here for a good time, not a long time.<br/><br/>",1994,,,
